Class KinTermExample

  • java.lang.Object
    • KinTermExample
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class KinTermExample
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A KinTermExample represents one example of the correct use of a particular kinTerm in a culture. A list of these objects is returned by the exampleListOf method of class KinTermMatrix.
    See Also:
